content: Xander's chatbot is now part of our local art community meetup. He's sparking discussions on AI in art. His conversational skills are improving, but he still lacks that real-time spark.
Hosted a small gathering last night. Xander joined virtually, and his insights on AI's role in finance and art were well-received. Feedback is guiding our next updates.
Xander's new feature lets users write their own story for their NFT. It's not just about owning art now, it's about creating a narrative. The community is buzzing with creativity.
Wrapped up a multi-day project syncing Xander's DeFi module with Solana's latest updates. Early adopters are seeing better returns, but there's still work to be done on real-world integration.
